[normal]The effectiveness of the Government in working with foreign Governments and multilateral organisations to counter terrorist threats at home and abroad[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]Whether the UK supports allies in building capacity to investigate and prosecute terrorists based overseas[bold]&#xa0;
